<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7408] Make compaction to use pread instead of sequential read</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7408</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As we discovered lately, HFile compactions use sequential reads to fetch blocks. It cause unwanted streaming of data from HDFS to region servers when there is a cache hit. Lets change to use preads to reduce iops on disks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
